{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I get out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I passed by through the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm not sure who it was, but I'm telling you now it was before or after that because I'm hurrying up because it should be the last tape.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I walked with a stick outside the front of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I saw two very large heaps-- pyramids of corpses in all sort of-- entangled.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was for a second thinking, maybe my father is amongst them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I couldn't stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had to go on-- go on, sort of shuffle on slowly, bit by bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I came across [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a barracks with darkened windows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I looked inside, hoping maybe to find something to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was darkened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I noticed another skeletal figure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as I drew nearer, the figure came closer with identical movements.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't recognize it at first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But obviously it was-- that's the first I saw myself after a long time, another skeletal figure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But instead of my spirits sagging at that time, it lifted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I waved to this image.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it smiled back when I said, this Muselmann is going to live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "For the rest, I was six weeks in this particular camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from there, we had the opportunity to go with the Jewish Brigade [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who registers that I could go to Israel or to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't want to go because I imagined I would have to stay-- stand next to my religious uncle, stand in prayers with somebody who hasn't experienced what I had experienced and that didn't want to know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But-- and I did register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the Jewish Brigade took us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
